# jobs/
#
# Background job / cron-task definitions (Phase 4).
#
# Planned jobs:
#   syncBusPositions.js  — polls MITRA every 15 s and updates cache
#   cleanupSessions.js   — removes expired session data
#   generateEtaCache.js  — pre-computes ETA for popular routes
#
# Job runner options to evaluate:
#   - node-cron (simple, no Redis needed)
#   - BullMQ    (Redis-backed, durable, retryable)
